		</Placemark>
		<Placemark>
			<name>Buckingham Street</name>
			<description><![CDATA["Araby"<br>[the street down which the narrator walks to get to the station]<br><br>"I held a florin tightly in my hand as I strode down Buckingham Street towards the station." (34)<br>]]></description>
