			<name>Eustace Street</name>
			<description><![CDATA["Counterparts"<br>[where Farrington works]<br>"Darkness, accompanied by a thick fog, was gaining upon the dusk of February and the lamps in Eustace Street had been lit" (89).<br>]]></description>
