			<name>Fleet Street</name>
			<description><![CDATA["Counterparts"<br>[where Farrington pawns his watch]<br>"Suddenly, as he was fingering his watch-chain, he thought of Terry 
Kelly's pawn-office in Fleet Street. That was the dart! Why didn't he 
think of it sooner?" (92)<br>]]></description>
