			<name>Temple Bar</name>
			<description><![CDATA["Counterparts"<br>[where the alley is that Farrington cuts through to get to the pawn office]<br>"He went through the narrow alley of Temple Bar quickly, muttering to 
himself that they could all go to hell because he was going to have a 
good night of it" (92-93).<br>]]></description>
