		<Placemark>
			<name>Westmoreland Street</name>
			<description><![CDATA["Counterparts"<br>[the busy street Farrington takes to get to the first bar]<br>"In Westmoreland Street the footpaths were crowded with young men and 
women returning from business and ragged urchins ran here and there 
yelling out the names of the evening editions" (93).<br>]]></description>
