			<description><![CDATA[<div dir="ltr">&quot;Counterparts&quot;<br>[the pub where Farrington meets Nosey Flynn]<br>&quot;Nosey Flynn was sitting up in his usual corner of Davy Byrne&#39;s and, when he heard the story, he stood Farrington a half-one, saying it was as smart a thing as ever he heard&quot; (93).</div>]]></description>
