			<name>Duke Street</name>
			<description><![CDATA["Counterparts" <br>[where Higgins and Nosey Flynn break off from the group of men who are going to continue to drink]<br>"At the corner of Duke Street Higgins and Nosey Flynn bevelled off to the
 left while the other three turned back towards the city" (94).<br>]]></description>
