			<name>Scotch House</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<div dir="ltr">&quot;Counterparts&quot;<br>[where the men go after Davy Byrne&#39;s]<br><br>&quot;Rain was drizzling down on the cold streets and, when they reached the Ballast Office, Farrington suggested the Scotch House. The bar was full of men and loud with the noise of tongues and glasses&quot; (94).<br><br>&quot;When the Scotch House closed they went round to Mulligan&#39;s&quot; (95).</div>]]></description>
