		<Placemark>
			<name>Ballsbridge</name>
			<description><![CDATA["Clay"<br>[where Dublin by Lamplight is located]<br>"From Ballsbridge to the Pillar, twenty minutes; from the Pillar to 
Drumcondra, twenty minutes; and twenty minutes to buy the things. She 
would be there before eight" (100).<br>(address from Gifford, pp. 77)<br>]]></description>
