		<Placemark>
			<name>Glasgow</name>
			<description><![CDATA["The Dead"<br>[where Mrs. Malins lives with her daughter]<br>"She lived with her married daughter in Glasgow and came to Dublin on a visit once a year. She answered placidly that she had had a beautiful crossing and that the captain had been most attentive to her.<br>She spoke also of the beautiful house her daughter kept in Glasgow, and of all the friends they had there" (190).<br>]]></description>
			<LookAt>
				<longitude>-4.175637638703361</longitude>
				<latitude>55.8666601038145</latitude>
