				<coordinates>-6.256527625166624,53.34660241275274,0</coordinates>
			</Point>
		</Placemark>
		<Placemark>
			<name>London</name>
			<description><![CDATA["The Dead"<br>[where the good singers are]<br>"--Oh, well, said Mr. Bartell D'Arcy, I presume there are as good<br>singers today as there were then.<br><br>--Where are they? asked Mr. Browne defiantly.<br><br>--In London, Paris, Milan, said Mr. Bartell D'Arcy warmly" (199).<br>]]></description>
