			<description><![CDATA["The Dead"<br>
[where the good singers are]<br>
"--Oh, well, said Mr. Bartell D'Arcy, I presume there are as good<br>
singers today as there were then.<br>
<br>
--Where are they? asked Mr. Browne defiantly.<br>
<br>
--In London, Paris, Milan, said Mr. Bartell D'Arcy warmly" (199).<br>]]></description>
