		<Placemark>
			<name>Mount Melleray Monastery</name>
			<description><![CDATA["The Dead"<br>[where Mrs. Malins's son is going]<br>"Mrs. Malins, who had been silent all through the supper, said that her son was going down to Mount Melleray in a week or so. The table then spoke of Mount Melleray, how bracing the air was down there, how hospitable the monks were and<br>how they never asked for a penny-piece from their guests" (200).<br>]]></description>
			<LookAt>
				<longitude>-7.855715239501516</longitude>
				<latitude>52.18884378610809</latitude>
