			</LookAt>
			<styleUrl>#m_ylw-pushpin71</styleUrl>
			<Point>
				<coordinates>-6.260346000000001,53.344475,0</coordinates>
			</Point>
		</Placemark>
		<Placemark>
			<name>Trinity College Dublin</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<div dir="ltr">&quot;The Dead&quot;<br>[where the cabman is directed to go]<br><br>&quot;--Do you know Trinity College?<br><br>--Yes, sir, said the cabman.<br><br>--Well, drive bang up against Trinity College gates, said Mr. Browne, and then we&#39;ll tell you where to go. You understand now?<br><br>--Yes, sir, said the cabman.<br><br>--Make like a bird for Trinity College.<br><br>--Right, sir, said the cabman&quot; (209).</div>]]></description>
			<LookAt>
				<longitude>-6.257177056766612</longitude>
				<latitude>53.34457550633176</latitude>
				<altitude>0</altitude>
