		</Placemark>
		<Placemark>
			<name>Nun&apos;s Island</name>
			<description><![CDATA["The Dead"<br>[where Gretta grandmother's house was]<br>"--Then the night before I left, I was in my grandmother's house in Nuns' Island, packing up, and I heard gravel thrown up against the window" (221).<br>]]></description>
			<styleUrl>#m_ylw-pushpin71</styleUrl>
