		<Placemark>
			<name>Bog of Allen</name>
			<description><![CDATA["The Dead"<br>[a place where Gabriel imagines the snow falling]<br>"It was falling on every part of the dark central plain, on the treeless hills, falling softly upon the Bog of Allen and, farther westward, softly falling into the dark mutinous Shannon waves" (223).<br>]]></description>
